78
00:04:09.869 --> 00:04:12.010
Kamu harus menuangkan minumanmu sendiri.

79
00:04:12.670 --> 00:04:13.939
Tuang sendiri-sendiri.

80
00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:39.729
Lagu ini.

81
00:04:42.099 --> 00:04:43.270
Aku membencinya.

82
00:04:43.739 --> 00:04:44.739
Apa?

83
