Astaga, dasar bodoh.

114
00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:39.419
Kalian sudah berulah saja di pagi buta.

115
00:06:39.620 --> 00:06:40.650
Astaga.

116
00:06:44.630 --> 00:06:45.789
Astaga.

117
