Aku masih sama seperti kemarin.

118
00:06:53.870 --> 00:06:55.070
Hore!

119
00:06:55.339 --> 00:06:56.469
Hore!

120
00:06:56.799 --> 00:06:57.969
Aku belum kembali.

121
00:07:02.779 --> 00:07:04.710
Bagaimana jika infeksinya menular kepadaku?

122
00:07:04.710 --> 00:07:06.279
Besok, aku hendak menemui pria.

123
00:07:06.279 --> 00:07:08.479
