00:12:02.140 --> 00:12:03.340
Baiklah.

211
00:12:03.340 --> 00:12:04.510
Bersiap, mulai!

212
00:12:24.130 --> 00:12:26.329
Hore! Aku menang!

213
00:12:26.970 --> 00:12:28.470
Aku akan berlari sampai sekolah!

214
00:12:28.870 --> 00:12:30.100
Hore!

215
00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.669
Hei, Choi Ban Do!

216
00:12:31.909 --> 00:12:33.569
Aku menang!

217
00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:45.590
Aku harus menemui Choi Ban Do lebih dahulu.

218
00:12:49.990 --> 00:12:52.289
